Rubber Guns, Chapter 1: After stopping a crook by dropping a wrecking ball on his stolen car Billy is moved to the Rubber Guns Squad.

The Once and Future Tarzan, Chapter 8: The storm is raising the water so they can launch the sub.

Chapter 12: I Burn Today: Vel saves Kyrra.
